  <title>Cogl.Primitive.texture_set_auto_mipmap</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function texture_set_auto_mipmap(primitive_texture: <link xref="Cogl.PrimitiveTexture">Cogl.PrimitiveTexture</link>, value: <link xref="Cogl.Bool">Cogl.Bool</link>): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for cogl_primitive_texture_set_auto_mipmap()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Sets whether the texture will automatically update the smaller
mipmap levels after any part of level 0 is updated. The update will
only occur whenever the texture is used for drawing with a texture
filter that requires the lower mipmap levels. An application should
disable this if it wants to upload its own data for the other
levels. By default auto mipmapping is enabled.</p>
  <p>Since 2.0</p>
